summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from Leonard Erikson and Hannah Erikson, his wife; Charles G. Erickson and Alma L. Erickson, his wife, Emil R. Wach and Minnie Wach, his wife,; Neal B. Treat and Ida May Treat, his wife; C.J. Peterson and Clara S. Peterson, his wife; Alfred Waeger and Mable Waeger, his wife; and Jesse S. Richards and Mable Richards, husband and wife, and Charles Doyle and Leona Doyle, husband and wife; to the City of Seattle, and laying off Cleopatra Place.
